data.name: Seek Love All Jetpacks
data.detailed_description:
You can get all of the following jetpacks directly.

KRONOS

We call him Kronos, how sophisticated he is, with a price of 499 and a jet power of 20.

HYPERION

This is Hyperion. The price of this jetpack is 999, he looks so cool! The jet power is 23.

THEIA

Her name is Theia, far more powerful than imagined! Her price is 1499 and jet power is 25.

ARES

He is Ares, the price is 2499, you will love him very much! His motivation is 27.

PROMETHEUS

This is Prometheus, his appearance is very beautiful, his price is as high as 2999, but his power is 30.

OUREA

Ourea is here. This is the most powerful jetpack, his price is 3999, and the jet power is 35.
